sequenceDiagram
 participant User as User
 participant App as 🅰 App Component
 participant Router as Router
 participant Weather as Weather Component
 participant Service as Weather Service
 participant API as Backend API
 
 User->>App: Load Application
 App->>Router: Initialize Routes
 Router->>Weather: Navigate to Weather Component
 Weather->>Service: Request Weather Data
 Service->>API: HTTP GET /api/weather
 API-->>Service: Weather Response
 Service-->>Weather: Weather Data (Signals)
 Weather-->>User: Display Weather Grid
 
 User->>Weather: Interact with Grid
 Weather->>Weather: Update Signals
 Weather-->>User: Reactive UI Update